Title: MULTIPLE FLAG VARIETIES OF FINITE TYPE  
Author: PETER MAGYAR, JERZY WEYMAN, AND ANDREI ZELEVINSKY 
Abstract: We classify all tuples of flag varieties with finitely many orbits under the diagonal action of the general linear group. 
